name: Dark Tattoo and Bodypainting
description: This model is trained on images of body painting and tattoos. It is helpful if you like to create fantasy villains or science fiction, cyberpunk, Punk, and Goth character images with dark and unique body art. I suggest you merge this checkpoint into whatever you’re working on. The base model for this is SD 1.4 so it should be possible to merge it into any 1.4 and 1.5-based model.
